<br>
I believe permarooting was done primarily because they wanted certain encounters to be happen under certain conditions - they didnt want people splitting hp outta room, etc.  Mobs sure as hell werent permarooted so that people could use cheesy agro tactics to avoid huge portions of meele damage.<br>
<br>
Anytime you fight a mob in such a way where the majority of your raid force can be in meele range of a mob while at the same time the mob isnt fighting back the majority of the time = exploit.<br>
<br>
Anyone who uses gimp tricks like this is stealing content from people who actually deserve it &amp; should be banned. <p><!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=412980">Lorcann</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--><br>
